{"tid":1333341,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉自絕食者tg】陳伯同咁多位絕食者有嘢啊","createTime":"2019-07-19T15:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T15:56:15.000Z","uid":281064,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ec957ab9d7368ce55d20af627c5043144f91adc0","tid":1333341,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"見條片post左一個晏就但都係唔係好多view<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢地呼籲既對象唔係年輕人 希望各位巴絲可以幫手傳出去比長輩們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好多謝一班咁明白事理又願意守護年輕人既長輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【守護孩子，齊來抗爭】行動<br />\n<br />\n75媽媽集會、714陳伯到沙田前線行動守護、715絕食同行苦行禮賓、717銀髮族遊行，顯示抗爭正凝聚各年齡各界別人士，一齊對準政權出發。呼籲你721繼續出泥聲援，遊行完勿散，到金鐘海富共商對策，於當晚如何守護年青人，繼續抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n日期：7月21日(日)<br />\n時間：遊行完(約晚上6至7時，到時決定，有人會在場的簡介)<br />\n集合地點：海富絕食站(金鐘a出口)<br />\n特別邀請參與對象：媽媽、銀髮族、傷健人士、神職人員、社工、律師<br />\n內容：共商方法，然後行動<br />\n*參加者請穿白衫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S_OdJcOCNHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS_OdJcOCNHk&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=36a3d36d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S_OdJcOCNHk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b388961d5bd6664e179b6d6c033586f5a39017","tid":1333341,"uid":146583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除咗升級裝備 仲有咩可以做？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入黎睇清香港局勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點評時下局勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://li